{"tid":178382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【生命作賭注】用左輪玩俄羅斯輪盤 巴西少女自轟爆頭死","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T23:33:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46670c73c702b611868d6e5252618334bf040251","tid":178382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"2017年03月29日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170329/large/1490774384_bd2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F1490774384_bd2c.jpg&h=716f2ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西一名15歲少女，周日取出叔叔的左輪手槍把玩，甚至賭命玩俄羅斯輪盤，結果一槍爆頭斃命。<br />\n<br />\n住在聖卡塔琳娜州（Santa Catarina）的克萊門蒂（Julia Lima Clemente），拿走叔叔的點38左輪手槍，與一名14歲友人在家內把玩。她曾兩度將手槍指向頭並扣下扳機，兩次都是射空槍，然而到第三次就自轟斃命。<br />\n生還的14歲友人向警方表示，兩人當時在談天，克萊門蒂突然拿槍出來玩俄羅斯輪盤。當局仍需等待法醫的檢驗報告。<br />\n克萊門蒂的媽媽知道女兒死訊後，因太過震驚而要送院治理。警方發現手槍的序號被刮走，現正追尋她的叔叔。家人對此非常傷心，並形容克萊門蒂是一位文靜少女，又稱「她不會玩危險的遊戲，她亦沒有抑鬱」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170329/56495436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170329%2F56495436&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=9c775d76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170329%2F56495436&h=b906910b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170329/56495436</a>"},{"pid":"521810131447b7c18d844aa3cf7b61164bc194cc","tid":178382,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"佢叔叔唔係好惦喎.......有槍都唔鎖住"},{"pid":"2b2c492c23eb9cbddab28eb237ab0cbca5b988da","tid":178382,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66f8ad801ea839a177ac91936b12712aff34cac9","tid":178382,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco